---
import Layout from "@/layouts/layout.astro";
import { Sparkles } from "lucide-react";
---

<Layout>
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center space-y-4 mb-16">
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-1.5 mb-4 border border-primary/10 bg-primary/5 rounded-full"
        >
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-primary/80">
            <Sparkles className="h-4 w-4 inline-block mr-2" />
            Made with Love
          </span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold font-display">Crafted by a Human</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground">
          Building tools that make email outreach more human
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mx-auto space-y-8">
        <p>
          I built ColdJot because I believe email outreach should be both
          personal and scalable. As someone who loves design and engineering, I
          wanted to create a tool that makes managing email sequences feel
          natural and effortless.
        </p>

        <p>
          What started as a way to manage my own email campaigns has grown into
          a complete toolkit for building relationships through email. From
          sophisticated sequences to analytics that help you understand what
          works, every feature is designed to help you connect more effectively.
        </p>

        <p>
          ColdJot is a one-person project, which means you're getting a tool
          crafted with care and intention. No venture funding, no growth hacks â€“
          just thoughtful features built for people who care about meaningful
          connections.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-16 text-center space-y-8">
          <p class="text-lg font-medium italic">
            "Thank you for supporting independent software. I'm committed to
            making email outreach more personal and effective for everyone."
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
            <img
              src="/zee.jpg"
              alt="Zee - Creator of ColdJot"
              class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full object-cover"
            />
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <img
                src="/signature.png"
                alt="Zee's Signature"
                class="h-12 mb-2"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
